## Health Metrics
```dataview
TABLE active_alerts, suppressed_alerts, micro_pending, response_rate, last_reflection
FROM "{{HERMIT_PATH}}/state"
WHERE file.name = "state-summary"
```

## Incomplete Sessions (Last 30 Days)
```dataview
TABLE date, task, status, tags
FROM "{{HERMIT_PATH}}/sessions"
WHERE id AND (status = "blocked" OR status = "partial") AND date >= date(today) - dur(30 days)
SORT date DESC
```

